    "translation": "展现万兽之王的气魄！喝下这瓶神奇的药水，废人也能瞬间变成强人，而强人将会变成神人！已知的副作用包括食欲暴涨和一些轻微的幻觉。",
    "stage": 1,
    "context": "this.m.Description = 'Take on the aspect of the beast of beasts! With this miracle draught, a cripple becomes as a strongman, and a strongman becomes as a god! Known side effects include an increased appetite and some minor hallucinations.'"
